**Morgan:** I'm not joking around. And I wasn't a //normal// sailor. I was obsessed.

**Simon:** No, no, no. Morgan, what I'm saying is I think you //were// right back then. That's the normal response any sailor would've had. I mean, that's what you said yourself, right?

